1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,000
Welcome to Bakudan Ramen Links Hub Admin. Manage everything customers see from one place. No coding required.

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:08,000
Dashboard: a quick overview. Action Required alerts real issues. KPI tiles show live button counts and clicks. Quick Actions give one-click access.

3
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:12,000
Pages: control center for every page. Green badge means public Customer Link Hub. Purple badge means private Staff Training. Click Edit to open.

4
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:16,000
Buttons tab: manage every button. Save as Template to reuse a page structure. Drag and drop to reorder. Each button has Visible, Enabled, Featured toggles.

5
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:20,000
Destination Types: External Website, Phone, Email, Maps. Toast Online Ordering. Call This Location auto-fills from your Locations data.

6
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:24,000
Sections: group buttons like Order Online or Rewards headers. Every button belongs to one section. Create, rename, reorder, hide, schedule, or delete.

7
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:28,000
Page Settings: title, URL slug, visibility, SEO. Google preview updates live as you type. Character counters for SEO title and meta description.

8
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:32,000
Templates: save a page as Template once, reuse for new stores. Create Page from Template in one click with title and slug.

9
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:36,000
Campaigns: track marketing initiatives across shortlinks. Clicks roll up from all shortlinks. Delete a campaign and its shortlinks still work.

10
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:40,000
UTM Builder: track which channel drives clicks. Preview URL updates live. Copy URL or create Shortlink plus QR code. Changing destination does not change QR image.

11
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:44,000
QR and Shortlinks: library of all shortlinks. Each has QR image, click count, and active status. Download QR as PNG.

12
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:48,000
Locations: single source of truth for The Rim, Stone Oak, Bandera. Phone, address, Toast links, hours. Call This Location reads from here.

13
00:00:48,000 --> 00:00:52,000
Staff Training: private page. Works like Customer Link Hub but is unlisted, no index, and never appears on public pages. Internal Use Only.

14
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:56,000
Scheduling: combined calendar view of everything with start or end dates. See which pages are about to go live or expire.

15
00:00:56,000 --> 00:01:00,000
Blog Composer: write posts with ready-made templates. Rich text editor with emoji. Social caption and hashtags. Schedule auto-publish.

16
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:04,000
SEO Manager: overview of every page SEO. Red alerts for missing title or description. One-click Edit to fix.

17
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:08,000
Analytics: real page view and click numbers. Total buttons, live versus hidden, views and clicks in 24 hours.

18
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:12,000
Settings: global Instagram and Facebook links, headline text, marketing copy. Users: Super Admin, Marketing Manager, Store Manager, Viewer.

19
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:16,000
Customer Service: post temporary Service Notices as banners. Set type, scope, start and end dates. Note: Admin create and edit currently saves locally in the browser.

20
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:20,000
Audit Log: every change is recorded with who did what and when. If something looks wrong, check here first.

21
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:24,000
That completes the tour. Core modules are live today. Forms, Automations, and Media Library are partially functional. Thank you for watching.
